news.headline: Princeton in Palm Beach: Yacht Club Cocktails and Lookahead to CorpGov Forum at Reunions 2026
news.summary: Princeton alumni gathered at the Palm Beach Yacht Club on December 23rd to toast the holiday season and the 2nd Annual Princeton CorpGov Forum, scheduled during 2026 Reunions.
news.article_text:
Princeton alumni gathered at the Palm Beach Yacht Club on December 23rd to toast the holiday season and the 2nd Annual Princeton CorpGov Forum, scheduled during 2026 Reunions.

The first Princeton CorpGov Forum was hosted together with The New York Stock Exchange and Goldman Sachs, held on May 22, 2025, at The Nassau Inn in Princeton, New Jersey.

Looking Ahead: The 2nd Princeton CorpGov Forum will be held in partnership with Princeton University’s Economics Department on Thursday, May 21, 2026.
